<td>audiant</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>Like the indicative, active personal endings may be replaced by passive personal endings. <i>Porter</i> can be translated as "Let me be carried" or "May I be carried." Hortatorily, <i>Portēmur</i> can be "Let us be carried."</p>
